                <i class="fa-solid fa-quote-left"></i>
              </span>
              <span class="is-size-6-mobile has-text-justified">
                FUHSO will be a world-class University that nurtures excellence in training healthcare professionals
                through innovation, cutting-edge research, and development, leading to the graduation of highly
                sought-after healthcare professionals.
              </span>

            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

